{"id":266397,"date":[{"year":1952,"month":6,"day":2}],"page":"7","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"文化广场","column":"","genre":"","count":"301","ytitle":"","mtitle":"人类的鲜花和嫩叶","ftitle":"","authors":["任钧"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"任钧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"初夏的公园里:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处是五颜六色的鲜花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所有的枝头都披满了嫩叶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"初夏的公园里:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(每逢晴朗的假日)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处是披着红领巾的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男娃娃和女娃娃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们来自学校、里弄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来自劳动人民的家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在暖洋洋的轻风里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明晃晃的阳光下:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灿烂的鲜花在微笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嫩叶不断地舞蹈在高高的枝桠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在暖洋洋的轻风里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明晃晃的阳光下:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草地上，水池旁——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小朋友们也在唱歌、跳舞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开会、玩耍……，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听吧:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一阵风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一根草、每一朵花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛都在告诉我们——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在毛泽东时代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在祖国大花园里:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这些男女娃娃们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是朵朵鲜花和嫩叶呵!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而且，毛泽东正是人民的太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在他的光和热的临照下:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们都将生长得又红又白，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"聪明、美丽……，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千百倍赛过公园里的鲜花和嫩叶!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入3号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1952\\06\\5262070301.JPG\">"}]}